Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:11420,12810}I want to be pretty…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:14010,19000}I want to wear nice clothes and be more beautiful than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:19000,23980}If I do, that person will turn around and look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:24410,27610}He'll turn around because I'm pretty.
