Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:34.13,Black Title,,0,0,0,,{TIME:29630,34130}{\fs150\pos(906,346)}Yuuko
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:44810,45900}Doi…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:53020,54040}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:54640,56780}Oh, Mayumi! You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:59440,61200}Oh, you look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:61200,63040}You look really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63860,68060}My papa just came back and brought lots of western clothes with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:68060,71050}Must be nice having a father like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71050,74040}He brought accessories with him too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:74520,76410}That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:76410,81290}It's nothing special really, when he\Ncomes back he never stops talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81290,83000}What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:83000,84140}I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84540,88800}I guess you're right, I should be happy that he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88800,90610}He got back in time for my birthday, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91280,93320}So, you're coming to my party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93320,94880}– Yeah!\N- Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94880,96050}You're coming too, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96250,98280}Well… I… of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99160,101020}Are there boys coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101020,103740}There are, Doi already said he is coming but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104020,106910}Mayumi! Are you going out with Doi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107340,108360}Of course not…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108360,110080}No way! You're going out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110080,112080}No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112080,114080}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115120,116590}I said that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:02:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117080,122090}We just talk at school all the time and he's helped me a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131890,134140}What? You've cleaned the blackboard for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134980,137490}I completely forgot, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139210,141010}He has such a kind voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141700,144960}After that I became curious about Doi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145540,150250}Whenever I looked at him,\Nhe was already looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151280,153000}Was that a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156410,159000}I have nothing to wear…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164460,165810}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173260,174320}Oh, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179240,179900}It's so pretty…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180840,184770}You can't, we don't even know who it's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185300,188170}It might have been delivered to the wrong house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188610,193160}That's not all, that one piece makes me uncomfortable…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217810,219030}It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219690,222720}It's almost like it was made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233980,235210}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235460,240170}Hey, Mama, is it okay for me to wear that to Mayumi's birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240170,241090}No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241860,246900}Why? Do you want them all to laugh at me for wearing my own weird clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246900,248980}You've already got lots of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248980,250800}You just bought some more the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250800,253800}That's not fair! Please, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254410,258560}You're just going to your friends house, why do you need to get all dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258560,260110}Stop being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263900,267250}I have to go… I have to…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267860,268650}Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268650,269030}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269560,270490}Hashimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271480,272610}Doi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273290,277290}Hey, you're going to the party today too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277290,277920}Y-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278280,281260}What a relief! I was invited too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281760,284430}This'll be the first time I see you in your own clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285090,287890}Well… I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288960,290280}I don't want to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291260,292810}I don't want to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293340,295810}I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298680,302230}It would've been nice if I could go wearing that one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303900,305290}Wh-What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309840,313940}No way! Mama said she closed it properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320680,323980}It's Mama's fault… all her fault…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323980,326300}All hers…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328300,330000}Yuuko sure is late, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330000,331530}She even said she was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344800,345960}Hashimoto…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347960,352240}Hey, Doi, let's go and play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352720,355340}It's my birthday today, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355340,356000}Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357620,359580}Yeah, okay. We'll bring Hashimoto too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363330,366760}Only I have to die…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371120,372720}Only me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375000,377360}Only I have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380680,381890}Doi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382120,382810}Doi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382810,383400}Doi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383890,385860}Doi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387890,390360}Doi… look at me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403010,408220}I was discharged a few days later and\Nfound out that Doi had transferred schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408720,413380}After talking to otther boys,\Nthey told me that he like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414300,417520}If I hadn't worn that dress,\Nthat wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417890,422640}But, I still can't get rid of the regret I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423040,430520}After yesterday's dance, the one piece that\Nshould have disappeared was back in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432520,436000}I still haven't checked properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436000,438000}I'm too scared to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438000,446440}Because I'm still scared of that eerie\None piece, everyday is filled with fear.
